<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="AllGenres_style.css" />
    <link rel="icon" href="images/open-book.png" />
    <title><%=title%></title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="nav_bar">
      <nav>
        <a href="Home"
          ><img src="images/logo.jpg" alt="Bookly Logo" class="nav_logo"
        /></a>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="Home">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="Genres">Genres</a></li>
          <li><a href="Recommendations">Recommendations</a></li>
          <li><a href="personalbooks"><%=name%></a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="quote">
      <h1>“Whatever our souls are made of, his and mine are the same.”</h1>
      <h3>
        -Emily Bronte- <br />
        <i>Wuthering Heights</i>
      </h3>
    </div>

    <hr />

    <div class="main-div">
      <h4>Featured Book:</h4>
      <div class="book-info">
        <a
          href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/50027029-you-deserve-each-other"
          target="_blank"
        >
          <img src="images/deserve.jpg" alt="You Deserve Each Other"
        /></a>
        <div class="book-desc">
          <h2>You Deserve Each Other</h2>
          <p>
            When your nemesis also happens to be your fiancé, happily ever after
            becomes a lot more complicated in this wickedly funny,
            lovers-to-enemies-to-lovers romantic comedy debut.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr />

    <div class="main-div">
      <h4>Signs Your Next Read Should be Romance:</h4>
      <div class="signs">
        <div class="sign">
          <img src="images/emotions.png" alt="Emotional">
          <p>You're Emotional</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sign">
          <img src="images/in-love.png" alt="in love">
          <p>You love Love</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sign">
          <img src="images/passion.png" alt="Passionate">
          <p>You're Passionate</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <img src="images/logo.jpg" alt="Bookly Logo" class="footer-logo" />
      <p>Our goal at Bookly is to help you decide on your next read.</p>
      <p>Follow us for more:</p>
      <div class="socials">
        <a
          href="https://www.facebook.com/mariajane.wehbe.9"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer noopener"
          title="Facebook"
          ><img src="images/facebook-brands.svg" alt="Facebook"
        /></a>
        <a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/mariajanewehbe"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer noopener"
          title="Instagram"
          ><img src="images/instagram-brands.svg" alt="Instagram"
        /></a>
        <a
          href="https://twitter.com/mariajane_wehbe"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer noopener"
          title="Twitter"
          ><img src="images/twitter-square-brands.svg" alt="Twitter"
        /></a>
        <a
          href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/37042627-maria-jane"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer noopener"
          title="Goodreads"
          ><img src="images/goodreads-brands.svg" alt="Goodreads"
        /></a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
